quests.description: It is time for us to confront Fatalis. We, along with every nation and organization known, shall rid this world of this fabled scourge. When you're ready, we'll set sail.

quests.name: Jagras of the Ancient Forest
quests.description: Zorah Magdaros's appearance has brought about changes in the local ecosystem. Head into Jagras territory to investigate, and take them out if necessary.

quests.name: A Kestodon Kefuffle
quests.description: Zorah Magdaros's appearance has driven a herd of Kestodon to new territory. We'll need you to go out and thin that herd of head-butters.

quests.name: The Great Jagras Hunt
quests.description: Things I'm not interested in writing in my daily report: "Researchers swallowed whole by Great Jagras." Take it out before I actually have to write it!

quests.name: Bird-Brained Bandit
quests.description: The Kulu-Ya-Ku uses its dexterous forearms to carry objects. Left unchecked it's liable to run off with crucial supplies. Step one of rebuilding a secure camp is hunting that thief!

quests.name: Urgent: Pukei-Pukei Hunt
quests.description: That Pukei-Pukei is none too pleased to have that slag in its territory. It'll be even less pleased if we send in our scholars to research it. Looks like we have to put it down.

quests.name: The Best kind of Quest
quests.description: Something surely left by Zorah Magdaros was discovered out in the Wildspire Waste. Fifth Fleet hunters: Keep our scholars safe as you escort them out to investigate this new evidence.

quests.name: Sinister Shadows in the Swamp
quests.description: A young scholar has gotten separated from his escort out in the Wildspire Waste. Find him and escort him back to base. Neutralize any large monsters that pose a threat.

quests.name: Flying Sparks: Tobi-Kadachi
quests.description: Oh, my! That Tobi-Kadachi sure is getting in the way of progress! You hunters will never get a hold of these specialized tools I'm making if I become its dinner!

quests.name: The Encroaching Anjanath
quests.description: As we're gearing up to capture Zorah Magdaros, we need to secure Astera as much as we can. It's too much of a risk to have that Anjanath roaming so close to base.

quests.name: One for the History Books
quests.description: At dawn we'll attempt what no one in history has dared: Capture an elder dragon! Make your preparations and proceed to the site. May the Sapphire Star guide us all.

quests.name: Ballooning Problems
quests.description: ...I'm sorry, I just retched thinking about that monster's face. Seriously, you'll be doing it a favor...and us too. Hunt it and the Airship Engineer will have everything he needs.

quests.name: Radobaan Roadblock
quests.description: The bones covering Radobaan's body are gonna be tough to get through, but if we want to continue our survey of the Rotten Vale, you'll need to find a way!

quests.name: Legiana Embodiment of Elegance
quests.description: You already know how I feel about that intolerable creature. As long as it controls the skies in the highlands, we'll never be able to make our descent. Do take care of it, won't you?

quests.name: Into the Bowels of the Vale
quests.description: ...... Certain death awaits you in the depths, but so does the key to finding Zorah Magdaros. A fair trade-off if you ask me.

quests.name: A Firey Throne Atop the Forest
quests.description: The First Wyverian's not gonna spill the beans about Zorah until we stand on top of the food chain. That means we gotta hunt us a Rathalos! ...Does that mean we have to eat it too?

quests.name: Horned Tyrant Below the Aands
quests.description: The First Wyverian's not gonna spill the beans about Zorah until we stand on top of the food chain. That means we gotta hunt us a Diablos! ...Does that mean we have to eat it too?

quests.name: A Colossal Task
quests.description: The operation is set to commence in the Everstream. Do everything you can to force Zorah Magdaros out to sea. We must not fail! May the Sapphire Star light our way!

quests.name: Invader in the Waste
quests.description: A Pukei-Pukei in the Wildspire Waste!? As if that's not already weird enough, this one's extra tough. We've gotta get to the bottom of this! Be careful, Partner!

quests.name: Tickled Pink
quests.description: A powerful Anjanath's been sighted! Their kind's the gold— pink?—standard for New World monsters. We can't let this chance at an ideal sample slip away. Go hunt it ASAP!

quests.name: Old World Monster in the New World
quests.description: We've finally tracked down the source of those mysterious tracks. Report to the Coral Highlands and seek it out! I'll be expecting your report as soon as you're done!

quests.name: A Wound and a Thirst
quests.description: The Nergigante's long eyed us from the far side of the Elder Crossing, but now we have a lead on its whereabouts. If we can study it, it may reveal the Crossing's true nature.

quests.name: Kushala Daora, Dragon of Steel
quests.description: The elder dragon tracks in the forest? Kushala Daora. I'm sure of it. We know it's in the Elder's Recess. For the safety of everyone in Astera, we're counting on you!

quests.name: Teostra the Infernal
quests.description: It's Teostra that stalks the Waste—Emperor of flame. And now it sits in wait in the Elder's Recess. Go to it, hunter, and end its searing reign!

quests.name: Hellish Fiend Vaal Hazak
quests.description: I'm absolutely positive that the effluvium is controlled by Vaal Hazak. Now to prove my theory once and for all. Go to the vale and seek out Vaal Hazak!

quests.name: Land of Convergance
quests.description: An immense energy flows through the New World, and we've found where it all leads to. Go with the Seeker and find out what's there. May the Sapphire Star guide us all.

quests.name: Baptism by Ice
quests.description: Ready to get exploring, Pard? I can hardly imagine what secrets are hidden beneath the snow! I'll find a place for the airship to land, you secure the area!

quests.name: Banbaro Blockade
quests.description: I've arranged a shipment of supplies from Astera, which should arrive at any moment. We'll need you to secure the Hoarfrost Reach to ensure it arrives safely. Don't forget to bundle up.

quests.name: Ready to Strike
quests.description: The scoutflies are useless with that Viper Tobi-Kadachi around. Get in there and do what you do best so we can keep pushing forward.

quests.name: No Time for Naps
quests.description: Target: Nightshade Paolumu. Reports indicate that first contact resulted in extreme drowsiness. That's where the report ends... Let's get to it, uh, Partner! Excited to see what you can do!

quests.name: Play Both Ends
quests.description: Target: Coral Pukei-Pukei. Reports indicate that first contact was greeted with blasts of...water? That's where the report ends... Let's get to it, uh, Partner! Excited to see what you can do!

quests.name: Blizzard Blitz
quests.description: Reports have been coming in about a Barioth roaming around the Reach. Those two are still examining the wreckage, but we'll need them to retreat for now. Get out there and bring them back safely!

quests.name: Ever-present Shadow
quests.description: Velkhana's arrival in the New World has thrown the ecosystem out of whack. I guess it was inevitable that a monster like a Nargacuga would show up. Get out there and take care of it.

quests.name: The Scorching Blade
quests.description: Velkhana's arrival in the New World has thrown the ecosystem out of whack. I guess it was inevitable that a monster like a Glavenus would show up. Get out there and take care of it.

quests.name: Absolute Power
quests.description: New monsters are popping up everywhere due to Velkhana's influence, even in the Rotten Vale. Head out and investigate this Tigrex. Be cautious of its piercing roar.

quests.name: A Smashing Cross Counter
quests.description: New monsters are popping up everywhere due to Velkhana's influence, even in the Elder's Recess. Head out and investigate this Brachydios. Be cautious of its explosive slime attacks.

quests.name: A Tale of Ice and Fire
quests.description: Thanks to everyone's diligent efforts, we know that Velkhana is in the Elder's Recess. We don't know why it's there, but we need our best hunters on the job. That means you!

quests.name: When the Mist Taketh You
quests.description: Leave finding the Tracker to me. In the meantime, secure the area by taking care of that Legiana! Be careful though, there's something off about this one...

quests.name: The Thunderous Troublemaker!
quests.description: The convoy from Astera is approaching the Hoarfrost Reach, but we need to secure its route. Our favorite troublemaker is back, and someone needs to teach it a lesson!

quests.name: The Disintegrating Blade
quests.description: As soon as Velkhana left, monsters everywhere started getting riled up. We're short on manpower, and we need a hunter to secure the defense convoy's route to Seliana. Start by taking out the Glavenus subspecies!

quests.name: Bad Friends, Great Enemies
quests.description: As soon as Velkhana left, monsters everywhere started getting riled up. We're short on manpower, and we need a hunter to secure the defense convoy's route to Seliana. Start by taking out the Odogaron subspecies!

quests.name: The Defense of Seliana
quests.description: Velkhana is closing in on Seliana! Man the Dragonrazer and drive that thing back! All of Seliana is counting on you, Sapphire Star!

quests.name: The Iceborne Wyvern
quests.description: We may have protected Seliana this time, but we still have no idea if and when Velkhana will return. It's time to take the fight to the beast before it recovers! Gear up and head out! And BE CAREFUL!

quests.name: The Second Coming
quests.description: Hah, look who's back to wreak havoc. This guy thinks he owns the place, but he's about to get a real rude awakening, right, Fiver? Get in there and send 'em packin'!

quests.name: Under the Veil of Death
quests.description: Something strange is going on... A Vaal Hazak has shown up in the Ancient Forest. Reports state that something is...off about it. What's it doing outside the vale? At any rate, be careful!

quests.name: A Light From the Abyss
quests.description: The Commission has discovered a never-before-seen elder dragon in the Coral Highlands. No solid info to go on, other than reports of an ominous light radiating from the highest plateau...

quests.name: To the Guided, A Paean
quests.description: Board the ship when you're ready. It's time we wrap up all loose ends. Who knows what we'll find when we land, but I know you'll be ready. You always are.

quests.name: Paean of Guidance
quests.description: The time has finally come to face Shara Ishvalda. I wish I could be there to have a good look at it... But this is a job only you're capable of. Good luck.

quests.name: Return of the Crazy One
quests.description: What!? A Yian Garuga!? According to my notes, these monsters will pick a fight with just about anything! It also says be careful around its supersonic roars. This is gonna be exciting, Pard!

quests.name: Sleep Now in the Fire
quests.description: This assignment is only for the few heroic hunters who can handle the rigors of being a true master hunter. Show everyone what you're capable of! (Completing this quest unlocks the MR cap limit)

quests.name: Big Burly Bash
quests.description: This assignment is only for the few heroic hunters who can handle the rigors of being a true master hunter. Show everyone what you're capable of! (Completing this quest unlocks the MR cap limit)

quests.name: To the Very Ends with You
quests.description: I know you've been waiting for this, and I bet Nergigante has, too. You guys are basically joined at the hip. But it's time to end this. Go get 'em, Hunter! (Completing this quest unlocks the MR cap limit)

quests.name: Butting Heads with Nature
quests.description: Blasted Kestodon! Every single time we go out to collect samples, those annoying creatures knock us on our tushes! I wish they'd butt out of our research!

quests.name: A Thicket of Thugs
quests.description: One of my field researchers wants to collect brightmoss to study. Only problem is, it's mostly found in caves. Guess what else is mostly found in caves? That's right...Jagras!

quests.name: Fungal Flexin' in the Ancient Forest
quests.description: Supplements? At MY Canteen? Pfft! We're all organic, baby! If you need vitamin D, get some Gourmet Shroomcaps! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: Learning the Clutch
quests.description: The old man said that New World hunters need to keep innovating, and our latest innovation is the clutch claw, a new feature of the slinger. Time for you to get up to snuff on how to use it.
quests.objective: Learn the mechanics of the clutch claw

quests.name: The Great Glutton
quests.description: I'm sure by now you've seen the way Great Jagras swallow its prey whole. One's been spotted again in the forest. Take it out before one of my researchers gets gobbled up!

quests.name: Camp Crasher
quests.description: The other morning one of my researchers woke to his camp having been pilfered by one of those thieving Kulu-Ya-Ku. Do something about it before it ransacks another camp!

quests.name: Snatch the Snatcher
quests.description: The Kulu-Ya-Ku uses its nimble forearms to pick up stones and eggs. Monsters that use tools are exceptionally rare. I'd like you to catch one for closer study.

quests.name: The Pain from Gains
quests.description: My paw-thritis is acting up again. Years of Palico-ing will do that to you. The best remedy? Good ol' Gajau liver oil! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: Exterminator of the Waste
quests.description: I need you to go out to the Wildspire Waste and waste a few Vespoids...or as I like to call them, punchin' bags with wings. *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: Special Arena: Pukei-Pukei
quests.description: A new challenger: Pukei-Pukei, the Toxic Tussler, the Lickin' Machine! He won't listen when you say "no tongues"! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?

quests.name: Special Arena: Barroth
quests.description: A new challenger: Barroth, the Hulking Headbutt, the Skull- cracker! Lose to this guy, and your name is mud! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?

quests.name: Special Arena: Tobi-Kadachi
quests.description: A new challenger: Tobi-Kadachi, the Leaping Lizard, the Bite- master! He'll clean your clock with thunder shocks! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?

quests.name: Scatternut Shortage
quests.description: A Pukei-Pukei must have shown up because it's getting more and more difficult to gather scatternuts! We can't study them if the only specimens we can gather are covered in poison!

quests.name: The Current Situation
quests.description: Don't touch me! Don't touch me! *zap* I told you NOT TO TOUCH ME! A blasted Tobi-Kadachi has shown up and now I can't touch anything without getting— *ZAP* OUCH!

quests.name: Mired in the Spire
quests.description: The Carrier Ants out in the Wildspire Waste are extraordinary engineers. We've been trying to further our research of them but a Barroth appeared and mucked up our entire operation.

quests.name: The Piscine Problem
quests.description: The Iron Helmcrab is such a fascinating creature. Just kick it over and out pops a piercing pod! We'd love to study them more but not with a Jyuratodus lurking about!

quests.name: Prickly Predicament
quests.description: I'm confident the plants native to the waste will help us grow our Ancient Trees, but I need your help gathering them! *Unlocks a Botanical Research item on first time completion.

quests.name: Gettin' Yolked in the Waste
quests.description: You ready for leg day!? GOOD! You'll need 'em when you're running from that Apceros herd! Now go get me my purr-otein! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: Landing the Landslide Wyvern
quests.description: Barroth dwell in the marshes of the Wildspire Waste, but details of their activities, diet, and nesting habits remain unknown. Catch one to help shed light on the issue.

quests.name: Special Arena: Anjanath
quests.description: A new challenger: Anjanath, the Jaws of Death, the Stomp- asaurus! He's just stopped by for a quick bite! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?

quests.name: Special Arena: Rathian
quests.description: A new challenger: Rathian, the Queen o' Green, the Sky- borne Slasher! Don't get the lady angry; she's poison! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?

quests.name: Special Arena: Paolumu
quests.description: A new challenger: Paolumu, the Punishing Puffball, the Fear- igible! It may not be fair, but he's walking on air! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?

quests.name: Special Arena: Radobaan
quests.description: A new challenger: Radobaan, the Roto-Ravager, the Grinder! Better dodge fast, or you'll be boned! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?

quests.name: One Helluva Sinus Infection
quests.description: Our entire department is out with the flu because of that Anjanath. How could they not be? The Ancient Forest is covered from top to bottom with that nasty mucus!

quests.name: Gettin' Yolked in the Forest
quests.description: You ready for leg day!? GOOD! You'll need 'em when you're running from that Rathian! Now go get me my purr-otein! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: Royal Relocation
quests.description: The samples I need to further my Ancient Tree research are right under a Rathian's nest. Perhaps you can move it for me? *Unlocks a Botanical Research item on first time completion.

quests.name: It's a Crying Shamos
quests.description: I almost feel bad for 'em. Those scrawny little monsters don't even stand a chance. Go flex on 'em while I get the goods! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: A Tzitzi for Science
quests.description: We've heard talk of the Coral Highlands' Tzitzi-Ya-Ku, how it emits flashes of light to blind its enemies. We must know the mechanics involved. Field team, please hunt one for our studies!

quests.name: Sorry You're Not Invited
quests.description: This is sort of an odd request but there is a birthday party coming up this weekend and we're in desperate need of balloons. If you could help us out you'd be a real hero!

quests.name: What a Bunch of Abalone
quests.description: You ready for arms day!? GOOD! You're gonna need 'em to gather these ingredients I've had my eye on! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: White Monster for a White Coat
quests.description: Paolumu dwell in the Coral Highlands, but details of their activities, diet, and nesting habits remain unknown. Catch one to help shed light on this mysterious creature.

quests.name: Persistent Pests
quests.description: There's a spot that I'm certain hides the secret to new Ancient Tree growth but it's infested with Hornetaurs! *Unlocks a Botanical Research slot on first time completion.

quests.name: A Rotten Thing To Do
quests.description: I was work-k-king the Rotten V-Vale when a G-G-Great Girros z-z-zapped me from behind. I g-got out in one piece, but I'm still all t-t-tingly... Finish the j-j-job for me? P-Please!

quests.name: A Bone to Pick
quests.description: It's nearly impossible for any of our researchers to study fossils in the Rotten Vale because they keep getting stuck to that blasted Radobaan rolling around down there...

quests.name: On Nightmare's Wings
quests.description: Here at the Second Fleet, we've been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We're counting on you to take this quest!

quests.name: Special Arena: Legiana
quests.description: A new challenger: Legiana, the Slipstream Striker, the Wing leader! Remember, you can't spell flight without fight! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?

quests.name: Special Arena: Odogaron
quests.description: A new challenger: Odogaron, the Muscle Mutt, the Rex Who Wrecks! He'll bite your leg to fetch the stick inside! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?

quests.name: Special Arena: Rathalos
quests.description: A new challenger: Rathalos, the Red-Hot Raider, the Fire- starter! Forgive the fireballs; he likes his meals cooked! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?

quests.name: Special Arena: Diablos
quests.description: A new challenger: Diablos, the Sandy Stampede, Biggus Diggus! Don't hang around if he's underground! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?

quests.name: When Desire Becomes an Obsession
quests.description: They say that Rathalos possess the rarest of gems, but I'm having a hard to time obtaining one. I've already gone through ten or so of them with no luck. Oh well, bring me another!

quests.name: Redefining the "Power Couple"
quests.description: Here at the Second Fleet, we've been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We're counting on you to take this quest!

quests.name: Twin Spires Upon the Sands
quests.description: Did you know there's a species of insect that survives by burrowing into Diablos tails? No? Well neither do we! And we won't find out unless you go and bring us one to be sure!

quests.name: A Humid Headache
quests.description: This weather is so humid you could cut the air with a great sword! Our department could do with some climate control and I know just the monster that can provide some relief!

quests.name: Gone in a Flash
quests.description: Why are you still here? An elder dragon's been spotted and you're just hanging out!? Hurry up before it gets away! *Unlocks a new Specialized Tool on first time completion.

quests.name: Scratching the Itch
quests.description: This morning I awoke to a brilliant epiphany! I have an idea for something every hunter needs after a long day out in the field...Odogaron backscratchers!

quests.name: Man's Best Fiend
quests.description: I really miss my old pet. The days we spent going to the park, playing fetch. I long for that companionship... that loyalty. Please go out and find me a new one.

quests.name: The Meat of the Matter
quests.description: You ready for back day!? GOOD! You'll need to put your back into it to get all the ingredients on this list! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Pukei-Pukei
quests.description: A new challenger: Pukei-Pukei, the Toxic Tussler, the Lickin' Machine! He won't listen when you say "no tongues"! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Pukei-Pukei Ambush
quests.description: A major change in the ecosystem is driving monsters from their natural habitats. Head to the Wildspire Waste and begin your investigation of the invading Pukei-Pukei ASAP!

quests.name: Dodogama Drama
quests.description: Hey, we've gotten a report of an unusually fine monster specimen roaming around. We need to seize on this opportunity, so we need you to investigate ASAP!

quests.name: A Scalding Scoop
quests.description: I was out on assignment when a Barnos barfed something at me. Whatever it was it was HOT, painfully hot! But also the sells-lots-of-copies kind of hot! Help me get my story!

quests.name: A Meow for Help
quests.description: Every time I try to gather something for my meowster out in the Everstream, these Gastodon knock me on my tail! MEOW-CH! Can you lend a Felyne a paw here?

quests.name: Chef Quest! A Rotten Request
quests.description: These little monsters think you're playing with them! Show 'em what you're made of! Let's say... 10 reps? *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: Chef Quest! Pumped to Deliver
quests.description: Now that you've worked both your upper and lower body, are you ready to put it to good use!? GOOD! Let's Work! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: Stuck in a Rut
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Radobaan appearing in the Rotten Vale. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware of its rolling attacks!

quests.name: A Tingling Taste
quests.description: ...... Why do I want you to hunt a Great Girros? Well, I'll tell you later. I know, how devilish of me. Run along now...

quests.name: Loop the Paolumu
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Paolumu appearing in the Coral Highlands. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware of its airburst attacks!

quests.name: Say Cheese!
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Tzitzi-Ya-Ku appearing in the Coral Highlands. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its blinding flash attacks!

quests.name: Trespassing Troublemaker
quests.description: A major change in the ecosystem is driving monsters from their natural habitats. Head to the Wildspire Waste and begin your investigation of the invading Anjanath ASAP!

quests.name: Brown Desert, Green Queen
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Rathian appearing in the Wildspire Waste. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware of its poisonous tail!

quests.name: Up to Your Waist in the Waste
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Jyuratodus appearing in the Wildspire Waste. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware of getting stuck in the muck!

quests.name: A Crown of Mud and Anger
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Barroth roaming the Wildspire Waste. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its mud-caked attacks!

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Barroth
quests.description: A new challenger: Barroth, the Hulking Headbutt, the Skullcracker! Lose to this guy, and your name is mud! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Keep Your Hands to Yourself!
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Kulu-Ya-Ku roaming the Wildspire Waste. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its clever attacks!

quests.name: Stuck in Their Ways
quests.description: Those three crazy old scholars went to study a LIVE Tobi- Kadachi. Please go capture it before they hurt themselves! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: The Sleeping Sylvan Queen
quests.description: A major change in the ecosystem is driving monsters from their natural habitats. Head to the Ancient Forest and begin your investigation of the invading Rathian immediately!

quests.name: It Can't See You if You Don't Move
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Anjanath appearing in the Ancient Forest. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its fiery attacks!

quests.name: A Hair-Raising Experience
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Tobi-Kadachi appearing in the Ancient Forest. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its lightning speed!

quests.name: Googly-eyed Green Monster
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Pukei-Pukei appearing in the Ancient Forest. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its poisonous attacks!

quests.name: Hard to Swallow
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Great Jagras appearing in the Ancient Forest. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its gluttonous appetite

quests.name: Left Quite the Impression
quests.description: Doesn't the sight of Zorah Magdaros make your heart skip a beat? Let me assure you, seeing its scales close up is just as awe-inspiring. It's imperative that we study it more.

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Radobaan
quests.description: A new challenger: Radobaan, the Roto-Ravager, the Grinder! Better dodge fast, or you'll be boned! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Paolumu
quests.description: A new challenger: Paolumu, the Punishing Puffball, the Fearigible! It may not be fair, but he's walking on air! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Rathian
quests.description: A new challenger: Rathian, the Queen o' Green, the Skyborne Slasher! Don't get the lady angry; she's poison! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Anjanath
quests.description: A new challenger: Anjanath, the Jaws of Death, the Stompasaurus! He's just stopped by for a quick bite! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Tobi-Kadachi
quests.description: A new challenger: Tobi-Kadachi, the Leaping Lizard, the Bitemaster! He'll clean your clock with thunder shocks! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Chef Quest! Gajalaka Lockdown
quests.description: Meow my god! Are these lil' guys tryin' to flex on you? Show 'em what you're packin'! Let's say... 10 reps! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Pink Rathian
quests.description: A new challenger: Pink Rathian, the Burning Blossom, the Beauty Who Bites! Best not stop to smell the roses! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Two-horned Hostility
quests.description: Hey, we've gotten a report of an unusually fine monster specimen roaming around. We need to seize on this opportunity, so we need you to investigate ASAP!

quests.name: Bazelgeuse in the Field of Fire
quests.description: That eccentric trio has gone and done it again! Now that they've discovered the location of a Bazelgeuse, they're off to study it! Please hunt it before they get themselves hurt!

quests.name: Ruler of the Azure Skies
quests.description: The field team has spotted an Azure Rathalos patroling the skies. Subspecies like these are highly valuable to the Commission's research efforts. Get going, hunter!

quests.name: Ore-eating Occupier
quests.description: We've gotten a report of an unusually fine monster specimen roaming around. We need to seize on this opportunity, so we need you to investigate ASAP!

quests.name: Lavasioth, Monster of Magma
quests.description: Hey, we've gotten a report of an unusually fine monster specimen roaming around. We need to seize on this opportunity, so we need you to investigate ASAP!

quests.name: Odogaron Unleashed
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Odogaron appearing in the Rotten Vale. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware of its powerful claws!

quests.name: Talons of Ire and Ice
quests.description: There's a spot I'm certain hides the secret to growing Ancient Trees. Unfortunately, two nasty monsters are patrolling that area. *Unlocks a Botanical Research slot on first time completion.

quests.name: A Sore Site
quests.description: Ugh! Every time I go out to the highlands to observe my beloved Paolumu, that gnarly monster is there! Please do something! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.

quests.name: Legiana: Highlands Royalty
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Legiana appearing in the Coral Highlands. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its swift and icy attacks!

quests.name: A Cherry Wind upon the Reefs
quests.description: The field team has spotted a Pink Rathian stalking the local wildlife. Subspecies like these are highly valuable to the Commission's research efforts. Get going, hunter!

quests.name: RRRRRumble in the Waste!
quests.description: *sigh* I've already told you what I want you to do. Run along now and complete this quest if you want your new toy. *Unlocks a new Specialized Tool on first time completion.

quests.name: Well, That Diablos!
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Diablos appearing in the Wildspire Waste. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware of its charging attacks!

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Legiana
quests.description: A new challenger: Legiana, the Slipstream Striker, the Wingleader! Remember, you can't spell flight without fight! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Pretty In Pink
quests.description: The field team has spotted a Pink Rathian stalking the local wildlife. Subspecies like these are highly valuable to the Commission's research efforts. Get going, hunter!

quests.name: The Red and Blue Crew
quests.description: Here at the Second Fleet, we've been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We're counting on you to take this quest!

quests.name: Rathalos in Blue
quests.description: The field team has spotted an Azure Rathalos patroling the skies. Subspecies like these are highly valuable to the Commission's research efforts. Get going, hunter!

quests.name: Rathalos Rematch
quests.description: We've gotten a disturbing report of another unusually powerful Rathalos in the Ancient Forest. Let that red beast know who REALLY stands atop the food chain here!

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Black Diablos
quests.description: A new challenger: Black Diablos, the Dark Destroyer, the Horn Express! Run, don't walk, from this furious fiend! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Diablos
quests.description: A new challenger: Diablos, the Sandy Stampede, Biggus Diggus! Don't hang around if he's underground! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Azure Rathalos
quests.description: A new challenger: Azure Rathalos, the Sapphire Sultan, the True Blue Terror! Bow down to the king of all wyverns! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Rathalos
quests.description: A new challenger: Rathalos, the Red-Hot Raider, the Firestarter! Forgive the fireballs; he likes his meals cooked! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Uragaan
quests.description: A new challenger: Uragaan, the Rolling Rocket, the Chinstigator! Once he starts spinning, uragoner! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: Special Arena: HR Odogaron
quests.description: A new challenger: Odogaron, the Muscle Mutt, the Rex Who Wrecks! He'll bite your leg to fetch the stick inside! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...

quests.name: A Fiery Convergence
quests.description: Here at the Second Fleet, we've been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We're counting on you to take this quest!

quests.name: A Portent of Disaster
quests.description: Here at the Second Fleet, we've been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We're counting on you to take this quest!

quests.name: A Blaze on the Sand
quests.description: Here at the Second Fleet, we've been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We're counting on you to take this quest!

quests.name: Lightning Strikes Twice
quests.description: Yet another Kirin has shown up and you're just here, playing with your Palico!? We might never get this chance again to study it! Go go GOOOOOO!

quests.name: Stirrings from the Grave
quests.description: Vaal Hazak serves its purpose in the life cycle of the New World, but now that it has stirred from its nest of decay, it threatens to ruin the whole ecosystem. It must be stopped!

quests.name: The Eater of Elders
quests.description: Nergigante is one helluva beast, and still so much we don't know 'bout it. Which is why I need you! If we're lucky, we might get to see two elder dragons squaring off!

quests.name: Master of the Gale
quests.description: Did you know that some cultures worship Kushala Daora as a god of wind? Luckily, we're not one of them! I'm determined to study its mastery of flight...just think of the benefits!

quests.name: Hellfire's Stronghold
quests.description: Teostra. Just saying the name makes my quill tip quiver. Some believe it's bad luck to cut the fur from this regal beast, but for the sake of the future, we must study it!

quests.name: The Eater of Elders
quests.description: Nergigante is one helluva beast, and still so much we don't know 'bout it. Which is why I need you! If we're lucky, we might get to see two elder dragons squaring off!

quests.name: The Winds of Wrath Bite Deep
quests.description: We've got a Kushala Daora running 'round, tearin' things up. Seems like it was kicked out of its territory. Question is, what did the kickin'? Time to investigate!

quests.name: The Fires of Hell Bite Deep
quests.description: We've got a riled up Teostra on the warpath. Seems like it was kicked out of its kingdom. Question is, what did the kickin'? Time to investigate!

quests.name: Beyond the Blasting Scales
quests.description: This quest courts only those with absolute faith in their abilities. You face two abnormally powerful Bazelgeuse, Defeat them to prove you are a true master of the hunt!

quests.name: Thunderous Rumble in the Highlands
quests.description: This quest seeks only those with an unquenchable flame in their chest. Make for the Coral Highlands and investigate the beast swathed in lightning. Beyond it lies true glory.

quests.name: A Light Upon the River's Gloom
quests.description: Xeno'jiiva is such a marvelous, mysterious example of exotic monster biology. We could study it for a hundred years if we just had enough samples! That's your cue, Hunter.

quests.name: The White Winds of the New World
quests.description: To the hunter who has conquered every investigation, I offer this, the ultimate quest. Enter the Special Arena and take on the New World. Use all that lies before you, and claim glory.

quests.name: The Sapphire Star's Guidance
quests.description: To the unparalleled hunter, I offer this final quest. Return to the Elder's Recess and brave the elders' onslaught. Use all within your grasp to prove yourself master of the New World.

quests.name: Showdown: the Muck and the Maul
quests.description: Here at the Second Fleet, we've been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We're counting on you to take this quest!

quests.name: New World Sky, New World Flower
quests.description: Here at the Second Fleet, we've been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We're counting on you to take this quest!

quests.name: A Summons from Below
quests.description: Here at the Second Fleet, we've been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We're counting on you to take this quest!

quests.name: Beating Around the Bush
quests.description: One of my researchers is out in the Ancient Forest hiding in a bush because he's "afraid" of a Tobi-Kadachi. I know he's just dawdling about. Please dispatch the monster so he can get back to work!

quests.name: Can't Bring Yourself To It
quests.description: We're facing a rather unique issue at the moment. Research in the recess has come to a halt due to a rather rambunctious Dodogama. However, most of our hunters are refusing to hunt it because they think Dodogama are..."cute."

quests.name: Grinding my Girros
quests.description: It's already quite difficult to get ANY research done in the Rotten Vale as it is. Merely existing in the vale without proper protection is enough to end you. And now a Great Girros has shown up with its little minions to complicate our work. Hunter, if you would, please.

quests.name: All the Wrong Signals
quests.description: One of my researchers was out testing a prototype feature of the Surveyor Set when a Tzitzi-Ya-Ku mistook the flash as territorial threat. The researcher panicked and dropped the device. If we are to ever recover it, we'll need you to dispatch the creature first.

quests.name: Taster's Tour
quests.description: We've got reports coming in from all locations confirming the existence of some unusually tough monsters. Head to their locations and begin your investigations ASAP.

quests.name: Jyura In My Way
quests.description: I need to consult with the First Wyverians about this new decoration I want to create, but there's a Joora...Jeeura—a big ugly fish in the way! Be a dear and please take care of it, will you?

quests.name: Dragged Through the Mud
quests.description: Accounting has been going on and on about how much zenny we spend on laundry. Well perhaps if there wasn't a Barroth out in the wastes flinging mud everywhere we could stay within our budget!

quests.name: Wildspire Treasure Hunt
quests.description: We've got reports coming in from all locations confirming the existence of some unusually tough monsters. Head to their locations and begin your investigations ASAP.

quests.name: Trapping The Tree Trasher
quests.description: Tail shakes alive, this meownster is gettin' on my last nerve! Can you please go out there and smack that overgrown pot roast upside the head so we can get these ingredients? (Canteen ingredients added upon first completion.)

quests.name: Literary Thief
quests.description: One of those blasted Kulu-Ya-Ku has stolen a very dear book that I leant to a field researcher. Take care of that despicable creature at once. Oh, and I suppose check on the researcher if you have time...

quests.name: New World Problems
quests.description: It's nearly impossible to obtain a sample from the Ancient Forest without it being contaminated by that blasted monster's poisonous slobber! Please, Hunter. Deal with it, won't you?

quests.name: The Great Jagras Returns!
quests.description: I need to consult with the First Wyverians about this new decoration I want to create, but there's some bloated lizard standing in the way. Be a dear and please take care of it, will you?

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Banbaro
quests.description: A new challenger: Banbaro, the Ruler of the Reach, the Champ of Tramp! If you can't dig your own grave, he'll dig it for you! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Tobi-Kadachi
quests.description: A new challenger: Tobi-Kadachi, the Leaping Lizard, the Bitemaster! He'll clean your clock with thunder shocks! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Barroth
quests.description: A new challenger: Barroth, the Hulking Headbutt, the Skullcracker! Lose to this guy, and your name is mud! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Pukei-Pukei
quests.description: A new challenger: Pukei-Pukei, the Toxic Tussler, the Lickin' Machine! He won't listen when you say "no tongues"! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Greetings from the Tundra
quests.description: Bossman says he wants to examine some Young Butterburs, so do me a solid and grab some for me, will you? Says he'll upgrade the Harvest Box for you in return! (First completion upgrades the Harvest Box)

quests.name: Call of the Wild
quests.description: Those Wulg are an interesting bunch! They don't go in for the kill right away. Nope! They wait for a chance, and then call in their buddies to help. Maaan, I love researching!

quests.name: Ice Catch!
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and get me them materials and I'll see if I can sneak in an upgrade! (Upgrades the Ghillie Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: Taking Charge
quests.description: —and by the by, you've locked horns with the gigantic Banbaro, yes? Thick fur to protect against the cold, and those massive horns! Simply astounding, yes? Oh, and the way it char—

quests.name: Deep Snow Diver
quests.description: Beotodus is a fascinating piscine wyvern that has the ability to "swim" through the snow. How it is actually able to do this is a mystery. I must have more data on this creature!

quests.name: This Here's Big Horn Country!
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. It's vital that you go out and get me them materials so I can get to work! (Upgrades the Vitality Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: Anjanath Antics
quests.description: I swear, if I have to handle one more report covered in snot, I'm going to have a fit! Is there not anything that disgusting beast won't blow its mucus all over!?

quests.name: Bugger Off Bugs!
quests.description: I want to speak with a First Wyverian about a decoration I want to meld, but the Commander won't let me go out with all these "big scary" monsters around. Can you "hang a girl up?" as you kids say.

quests.name: No Laughing Matter
quests.description: Oh, dear...hahaha! One of my researchers *snicker* was attacked by a Radobaan and—as she was running away—all of her research notes got stuck to the tar on its body. So, as we speak, there's a Radobaan rolling around the vale with her life's work glued to it... BWAHAHAHA!

quests.name: Put That Red Cup Away
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. This mantle may be waterproof but it sure as heck ain't upgrade-proof! (Upgrades the Waterproof Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: Protip: Stay Hydrated
quests.description: Coral Pukei-Pukei possess specialized organs to store the water they consume. I'd like to have a closer look at it for my notes, so I'll have to call in a favor just this once, Hunter.

quests.name: Pink Power Grab
quests.description: The exodus of Legiana has created a power vacuum in the Coral Highlands. A rather fearsome Pink Rathian seems inclined to fill that void. However, her reign is having a detrimental effect on the food chain. I ask that you go out and usurp the throne, Hunter!

quests.name: The Plight of Paolumu
quests.description: As operations in the Hinterlands expand further, our researchers require gear that is not only well-insulated but comfortable for long hours of field work. I'm interested in having a prototype developed, however I'll need some materials before we can start.

quests.name: Feisty Girl Talk
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and get me them materials and I'll make sure your tools get a healthy upgrade! (Upgrades the Health Booster upon first completion.)

quests.name: Stick Your Nose Somewhere Else
quests.description: We've got reports coming in from all locations confirming the existence of some unusually tough monsters. Head to their locations and begin your investigations ASAP.

quests.name: Face Nightmares Are Made Of
quests.description: There I was, minding meow-n business, when suddenly the ugliest face I'd ever seen jumped out at me. I must have fainted, but when I came to, it was gone. I know it's still out there... Out there with its hideous face! Please, Hunter! I still have nightmares about it!

quests.name: A Queen At Heart
quests.description: I want to speak with a First Wyverian about a decoration I want to meld, but the Commander won't let me go out with all these "big scary" monsters around. Can you "hang a girl up?" as you kids say.

quests.name: Nighty Night Nightshade
quests.description: Tail shakes alive, this meownster is gettin' on my last nerve! Can you please go out there and smack that ugly thing upside its ugly head so we can get these ingredients? (Canteen ingredients added upon first completion.)

quests.name: Fool's Mate
quests.description: Dear Gog... One of my researchers is absolutely obsessed with a particular Rathian he has been observing. So much so that he rarely returns to base anymore to report. I ask that you do something about it before things get...weird.

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Nightshade Paolumu
quests.description: A new challenger: Nightshade Paolumu, the Sultan of Slumber, the Flightmare! Get caught in the sleeper hold, and it's lights out! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Paolumu
quests.description: A new challenger: Paolumu, the Punishing Puffball, the Fearigible! It may not be fair, but he's walking on air! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Pink Rathian
quests.description: A new challenger: Pink Rathian, the Burning Blossom, the Beauty Who Bites! Best not stop to smell the roses! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Rathian
quests.description: A new challenger: Rathian, the Queen o' Green, the Skyborne Slasher! Don't get the lady angry; she's poison! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Viper Tobi-Kadachi
quests.description: A new challenger: Viper Tobi-Kadachi, The Boss of Blight, the Number One Stunner! He bites you, you bite the dust! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Coral Pukei-Pukei
quests.description: A new challenger: Coral Pukei-Pukei, the Savage Sprayer, the Blast Master! Watch out or he'll take you to the cleaners! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Radobaan
quests.description: A new challenger: Radobaan, the Roto-Ravager, the Grinder! Better dodge fast, or you'll be boned! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Anjanath
quests.description: A new challenger: Anjanath, the Jaws of Death, the Stompasaurus! He's just stopped by for a quick bite! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: You Scratch Our Backs...
quests.description: Thanks to your efforts, we've made fellowship with the local Lynians! I'd like to pay them a visit, but a meddling Beotodus is in the way. Please, for science, assist me!

quests.name: By Our Powers Combined
quests.description: Our target of this joint operation is the fearsome Beotodus! First, drive a Popo out in the open to lure the monster out. Then when that frosty fishy takes the bait, we'll ambush it!

quests.name: Boaboa Constrictor
quests.description: Duuuude! I got these sick drafts cooked up! Just, uh, they need a few more tweaks. Yo, help me out with this quest, and stuff, and you can get a special ticket. Pretty sweet, right?

quests.name: Poison and Paralysis Pinch
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and get me them materials and I'll see if I can boost your tools with an upgrade! (Upgrades the Cleanser Booster upon first completion.)

quests.name: Analysis Creates Paralysis
quests.description: Can't...move... Bitten...by...a Viper...Tobi-Kadachi... Poison...seeping...into...my bloodstream... In...lots...of trouble... Help...me...please...!

quests.name: Looking For That Glimmer
quests.description: Bossman says he's got some theories about Gaia Amber that he'd like to test. In return for your help, he'll upgrade the Harvest Box. (Upgrades the Harvest Box upon first completion.)

quests.name: The Black Wind
quests.description: Some of the newly discovered monsters in the New World have been sighted in other locales. The shift in surroundings will most likely have a significant effect on their behavior, head to their location and investigate immediately.

quests.name: The Secret to a Good Slice
quests.description: Some of the newly discovered monsters in the New World have been sighted in other locales. The shift in surroundings will most likely have a significant effect on their behavior, head to their location and investigate immediately.

quests.name: Red and Black Acese
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and get me them materials I need and I'll make sure your mantle soars to new heights! (Upgrades the Glider Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: A Line in the Sand
quests.description: Our researchers are finding it nearly impossible to study the cacti out in the wastes. Even attempting to get close to a cactus patch triggers a Diablos attack from below...

quests.name: A Flash of the Blade
quests.description: —and by the by, you've crossed blades with the fearsome Glavenus, yes? The way it wields its gleaming, sword tail! Simply astounding, yes? Oh, and how it sharpens it in its—

quests.name: Simmer and Slice!
quests.description: Tail shakes alive, these meownsters are gettin' on my last nerve! Can you please go out there and smack those two upside the head so we can get these ingredients? (Canteen ingredients added upon first completion.)

quests.name: Legiana Left Behind
quests.description: Due to the Legiana migrating to the Hinterlands, there has been a shortage of specimen to study in the Coral Highlands. However, a straggler has been spotted recently. We can't let this opportunity go to waste!

quests.name: A Nasty Flesh Wound
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and snatch the materials I need and I'll sneak an upgrade into your tools! (Upgrades the Bandit Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: Swoop to a New Low
quests.description: Blasted Rathalos! Every time the field team tags an Aptonoth to track its behavior, this confounded creature swoops in and carries it off! It's almost as if it's doing it on purpose!

quests.name: Don't be a Jerk with the Jerky
quests.description: One of my less forward-thinking researchers has quite an affinity for snacks, especially Astera jerky. I've told him time and again to only eat them when necessary but now he's really in trouble. An Odogaron has attacked him and without any jerky, I'm afraid he may be done for...

quests.name: A Roar that Shook the Vale
quests.description: It's well-known that the Tigrex is a primitive flying wyvern, which means investigating its appearance in the New World could teach us much about other flying wyverns here!

quests.name: Runnin', Rollin', and Weepin'
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. It'll hardly be a challenge to upgrade your gear if you go out and get me the materials I need! (Upgrades the Challenger Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: Blast Warning In Effect!
quests.description: —and by the by, you've exchanged blows with the Brachydios, yes? Most clamor over its peculiar slime, but not I! No, I'm all about those fists! Yes, the way it strikes the ground and—

quests.name: Everyone's a Critic
quests.description: Whilst one of our artists was out trying to paint a landscape of the recess, a Lavasioth appeared out of nowhere and attacked. Though he survived the ordeal, his commissioned piece did not. Please make your way out there and secure the area so that he may continue his work.

quests.name: Begone Uragaan
quests.description: The infirmary is overflowing with researchers suffering from extreme vertigo. The cause? One of those blasted Uragaan rolling about. Go out there and put the brakes on its spinning!

quests.name: Secret of the Ooze
quests.description: I'd like to experiment with that peculiar slime the Brachydios secretes—oh, it'll be 100% safe, don't you worry! Heh... And if you help, I'm sure it'll help our Ancient Tree some, too! (Unlocks a Botanical Research slot on first time completion.)

quests.name: Nargacoulda, Shoulda, Woulda
quests.description: I should know better than to go out into the Ancient Forest without a hunter escort, but I didn't think a freakin' Nargacuga would be there! Why didn't anybody tell me!? Help me, PLEASE!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Tigrex
quests.description: A new challenger: Tigrex, the Rushing Rampager, the Emperoar! This monster puts the arm in harm! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Proud White Knight
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me them materials and this upgrade will have you bobbin' and weavin' like there's no tomorrow! (Upgrades the Evasion Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: Remember That One Time?
quests.description: So yeah, the Barioth...a violent snowstorm personified. It reminds me of this one time I had to go on a hunt for... You know what? Never mind. I'll leave this to you.

quests.name: The Purr-fect Room: Stone
quests.description: P.U.R.R. is in fur effect...with just one minor hiccup: a Tigrex! Nab that angry tabby while we sneak past to grab the goods! (Room decoration added upon first completion.)

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Legiana
quests.description: A new challenger: Legiana, the Slipstream Striker, the Wingleader! Remember, you can't spell flight without fight! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Brachydios
quests.description: A new challenger: Brachydios, the Guru of Goo, The Purple Pounder! Says he's looking for some chump called "Doodle." Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Odogaron
quests.description: A new challenger: Odogaron, the Muscle Mutt, the Rex Who Wrecks! He'll bite your leg to fetch the stick inside! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Uragaan
quests.description: A new challenger: Uragaan, the Rolling Rocket, the Chinstigator! Once he starts spinning, uragoner! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Rathalos
quests.description: A new challenger: Rathalos, the Red-Hot Raider, the Firestarter! Forgive the fireballs; he likes his meals cooked! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Diablos
quests.description: A new challenger: Diablos, the Sandy Stampede, Biggus Diggus! Don't hang around if he's underground! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Barioth
quests.description: A new challenger: Barioth, the Tusked Terror, The Baron of Blizzards! First everything's white, then it turns black! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Nargacuga
quests.description: A new challenger: Nargacuga, the Shadowy Slayer, the Nimble Ninja! If you can't see him, it's already too late! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Glavenus
quests.description: A new challenger: Glavenus, the Cauterizer, the Slasha- saurus! With this monster, every match is a split decision! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Festival of Explosions!
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me the materials I need and I'll make sure your gear's upgrade'll be straight fire! (Upgrades the Fireproof Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Fulgur Anjanath
quests.description: A new challenger: Fulgur Anjanath, the Shock-o-saurus, T-Wrecks! He's electric! Boogie Woogie, Woogie! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Blue Rathalos Blues
quests.description: Azure Rathalos are known to mark their territory with gashes by using their massive claws. As fascinating as this is to our ethology department, it's quite a headache for our geologists.

quests.name: The Purr-fect Room: Dark Iron
quests.description: P.U.R.R. is in fur effect...with just one minor hiccup, well, actually two: a double dose of depraved devil doggies! Put 'em on a leash so we can go in and get the goods! (Decor materials for your room added upon first completion.)

quests.name: The Purr-fect Room: Light Iron
quests.description: P.U.R.R. is in fur effect...with just one minor hiccup: an Acidic Glavenus! Bag us that Glavenus and we'll sneak past and snatch the goods! (Decor materials for your room added upon first completion.)

quests.name: This Corroded Blade
quests.description: —and by the by, you've dueled with the Acidic Glavenus, yes? How it sharpens that dull, acidic tail into a beautiful blade! Simply astounding, yes! Oh, and the way it winds up for an—

quests.name: A Shadowy Offender
quests.description: "I'm on the trail of an Ebony Odogaron. It's a ferocious monster that seems to have a thirst for battle. I must take care not—" (the rest of the note is torn...)

quests.name: Piercing Black
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me the materials I need and no monster will be knocking you around! (Upgrades the Rocksteady Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: In the Heat of the Moment
quests.description: It seems that one of our researchers was set on by a Black Diablos and during the encounter he spilt attractant all over himself. Now the lovesick beast is chasing him all over the wastes...

quests.name: Misfortune in the Forest
quests.description: Some of the newly discovered monsters in the New World have been sighted in other locales. The shift in surroundings will most likely have a significant effect on their behavior, head to their location and investigate immediately.

quests.name: These Azure Eyes See All
quests.description: We've got reports coming in from all locations confirming the existence of some unusually tough monsters. Head to their locations and begin your investigations ASAP.

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Ebony Odogaron
quests.description: A new challenger: Ebony Odogaron, the Overlord of Onyx, the Hell- hound that Pounds! He'll teach you to sit, roll over, and play dead! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Acidic Glavenus
quests.description: A new challenger: Acidic Glavenus, the Colonel of Corrosion, The Dino Dueler! There's no stoppin' once he gets to choppin'! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Black Diablos
quests.description: A new challenger: Black Diablos, the Dark Destroyer, the Horn Express! Run, don't walk, from this furious fiend! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Azure Rathalos
quests.description: A new challenger: Azure Rathalos, the Sapphire Sultan, the True Blue Terror! Bow down to the king of all wyverns! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Treasure in the Steam
quests.description: Duuuude! I got these sick drafts cooked up! Just, uh, they need a few more tweaks. Yo, help me out with this quest, and stuff, and you can get a special ticket. Pretty sweet, right?

quests.name: Duet of Rime
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and get me the materials I need and I'll hook you up with a cool upgrade! (Upgrades the Iceproof Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: Tundra Troublemaker
quests.description: —and by the by, you've come snout to snout with the Fulgur Anjanath, yes? How a brute wyvern could somehow make its way to the Hinterlands! Astounding, yes? How can it even swi—

quests.name: Noblefrost Hunter
quests.description: How that Legiana got a cloak of ice like that is a mystery, but it's nothing science can't solve! We'll need all the data you can get on that thing!

quests.name: Trap the Thunder Jaw
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me the materials I need and I'll upgrade your gear lightning-quick! (Upgrades the Thunderproof Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: Clashing Swords Upon The Rime
quests.description: Official records about Velkhana are non-existent, and much has yet to be confirmed about its ecology. But this is the perfect opportunity for us—er, YOU, to make history!

quests.name: The Harbinger of Clear Skies
quests.description: Sure, Kushala Daora wrecks things with its storms, but I think it gets a bad rap. I mean, after those storms, it's super sunny and everything! Help me change people's minds!

quests.name: Here Comes the Deathmaker
quests.description: ...... So, the stories are true. A Vaal Hazak, in the Ancient Forest. Time for you to get to work, Hunter. Run along, now.

quests.name: Royal Audience on the Sand
quests.description: A member of the Fourth encountered a Teostra in the Waste, one more terrible than usual. The emperor sits on its throne, waiting. Shall we pay him a visit?

quests.name: The Tyrant's Banquet
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and get me the materials I need and the status of your gear is sure to go up! (Upgrades the Apothecary Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: Lightning Crashes
quests.description: An unusual amount of lightning and radiance has occurred in the Highlands recently. This must be a sign that a Kirin is active in the area. You MUST look into this, Hunter!

quests.name: Memories of the Sea God
quests.description: Namielle is a truly terrifying beast, capable of summoning torrents as well as lightning! We must gather as much data as possible. I ask that you head out immediately, and of course, be careful!

quests.name: It's the Afterlife for Me
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. Your gear might be immune to abnormal status effects but it ain't immune to my upgrades! (Upgrades the Immunity Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: Wings of the Wind
quests.description: Black tornadoes have been spotted in the Elder's Recess. Analytics believes this is the work of a Kushala Daora, and a very nasty one at that. I'll leave this one to you, bud.

quests.name: Mark of the Sun
quests.description: The Huntsman and I tried to take on a Teostra, but it was too much for us. We need you to head out to the Elder's Recess and provide assistance. As in, you take care of it!

quests.name: Seething with Anger
quests.description: So I heard this new Bazelgeuse is supposed to be red-hot. But do you think it can match MY red-hot passion for life? Uh, DOUBT IT! Let's go out and cool down that fool!

quests.name: The Purr-fect Room: Silver
quests.description: P.U.R.R. is in fur effect...with just one minor hiccup: a Bazelgeuse! Maybe if you say its name three times, we can sneak in and get the goods! Go on, give it a try! (Decor materials for your room added upon first completion.)

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Gold Rathian
quests.description: A new challenger: Gold Rathian, The Queen of Sheen, the Lethal Lunar Lady! She may be golden but she'll leave you black and blue. Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Into the Palace of Flame
quests.description: A request to track down a Lunastra has come in! I wonder what it's like to be treated like an empress. Take this quest, mon étoile, and show me...

quests.name: Divine Surge
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me the materials I need and I'll make sure your gear is truly next generation! (Upgrades the Temporal Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: One Hot Night in the Spire
quests.description: Lunastra...I saw her just once and tried to express my feelings, but it was not meant to be. Oh, to be caressed by her flames... I need someone to tell her how I feel!

quests.name: The Storm Brings the Unexpected
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me the materials I need and I guarantee you'll just love this upgrade! (Upgrades the Affinity Booster upon first completion.)

quests.name: Hymn of Moon and Sun
quests.description: I've been going bonkers thinkin' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me the materials I need and I guarantee this upgrade will have massive impact! (Upgrades the Impact Mantle upon first completion.)

quests.name: Faraway Lorelei
quests.description: Gotta admit, Shara Ishvalda is one elder dragon that is a sight to behold. Still can't believe it led us all the way here. We still have much to learn, let's pay it another visit!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Silver Rathalos
quests.description: A new challenger: Silver Rathalos, the Glistening Gladiator, the Fireball Flinger! He reigns over the ring with a rain of fire! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Brute Tigrex
quests.description: A new challenger: Brute Tigrex, the Aggro Assaulter, the Bellowing Blitzer! He's talkin' trash with the moves to back it up! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Yian Garuga
quests.description: A new challenger: Yian Garuga, the Screamin' Demon, the Beaked Berzerker! You've never seen crazy like this before! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: Special Arena: MR Zinogre
quests.description: A new challenger: Zinogre, the Bug Zapper, the Thunder Clapper! When this pup gets to howlin', better throw the towel in! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!

quests.name: We Run This Town
quests.description: You've overcome everything thrown at you so far, why not just one more challenge? Come out of this unscathed, and no one will forget why you're the real Sapphire Star!

quests.name: Master Hunter of the New World
quests.description: You've had your rough patches, but you've become a shining beacon for the Commission. So here's to you, one last quest. May your name be etched in history!

quests.name: Up at the Crack of Dawn
quests.description: "Our friendly Kestodon have blown a gasket, so we let them cool off in your Arena. Research Commission friends, please see if they've settled down." (Translation by the Lynian Researcher)

quests.name: Challenge Quest 1: Beginner
quests.description: In the monster corner: Two fringed contenders guaranteed to ruffle your feathers! Below the belt shots are allowed! You're the only one with a belt, so watch out!

quests.name: Vespoid Infestation!
quests.description: Oh deeeear! I placed some monster repellent around here, but it started attracting giant Vespoids too! Someone, anyone, I need an exterminator!

quests.name: USJ Beginners Challenge!
quests.description: Hello everyone, and welcome to USJ! We're happy to introduce our latest quest attraction, perfectly suitable for beginners! Come on and enjoy yourselves!

quests.name: Chew The Fat
quests.description: Yo, got a quest for you, but don't worry, this is right up your alley. We got a couple of Great Jagras that need to be taken care of. Trust me, the rewards will be worth it.

quests.name: Where Sun Meets Moon
quests.description: I heard there's a period of time when diurnal and nocturnal endemic life meet, so I wanted to see for myself, but now I'm in a jam! (Special ticket and increased rare material rewards)

quests.name: Down the Dark, Muddy Path
quests.description: I heard rumors of a powerful monster dwelling in this place. One clad in an armor of earth. You must be like myself, seeking a rival that will force you to surpass your limits. It's time to fight!

quests.name: USJ: Gold Star Treatment
quests.description: USJ is pleased to bring you the most exciting attraction ever! Witness this grand world in all of its golden glory! You'll be presented with some fantastic equipment once you're done!

quests.name: Timberland Troublemakers
quests.description: I woke up early to go and fetch some Goldbloom, but I found a grumpy Anjanath standing in my way! Take care of him, will ya? (Rare material reward chance up, special ticket available)

quests.name: Challenge Quest 2: Beginner
quests.description: In the monster corner: A Paolumu and Tobi-Kadachi tag team! One zips and zaps while the other drifts and flips! Wouldn't you know it, they make good enemies, but better friends!

quests.name: USJ Expert Challenge!
quests.description: Hello everyone, and welcome to USJ! We're happy to introduce our latest quest attraction, perfect for those who can beat up a monster with one arm tied behind their back!

quests.name: USJ Beginners Challenge!
quests.description: Hello everyone, and welcome to USJ! We're happy to introduce our latest quest attraction, perfectly suitable for beginners! Come on and enjoy yourselves!

quests.name: Ya-Ku With That?
quests.description: Hunter, these two meownsters are su-purr good at stealing eggs and dropping wingdrakes in a flash. But purrhaps they'll make for good equipment too, mew get me?

quests.name: Greeting the Gluttons
quests.description: Huh? Yeah, this is a quest from the Meowscular Chef. Whoa, you'll go instead of me? Wow, thanks a bunch! To show my gratitude, the next meal's on me!

quests.name: Troubled Troupers
quests.description: "We Troupers are getting batterfanged by two Tzitzi-Ya-Ku. Please har-meow-nize with our warriors to wallop them into hightailing it!" (Translation by the Lynian Researcher)

quests.name: Every Hunter's Dream
quests.description: A hunter came by with a blueprint of a weapon he wanted. I still have the prints lying around, so if you want one of your own, get me the materials and I'll start workin'.

quests.name: USJ Expert Challenge!
quests.description: Hello everyone, and welcome to USJ! We're happy to introduce our latest quest attraction, perfect for those who can beat up a monster with one arm tied behind their back!

quests.name: Wicked Wildspire Warfare
quests.description: Do you know what'll happen if we get a couple of highly territorial monsters in one spot? No? Neither do I! Let's find out. Come out on top to earn Armor Spheres!

quests.name: Flesh Cleaved to Bone
quests.description: So...let me get this straight, you're going to step into the arena and get between Fido and its chew toy? Teaching it to play dead, are we?

quests.name: Kirin The Myth
quests.description: I looked left, it appeared on the right. I glanced behind me, it showed up in front of me. When I thought there was one of them, there were two. I'm outmatched here. This task is all yours.

quests.name: The Poison Posse
quests.description: They say the most beautiful of chalices are poisonous. But I don't think that applies to flying wyverns. But just in case, look into that for me.

quests.name: Midnight Mayhem
quests.description: "The heck, am I lost? I don't recognize this place. Oh well, I might as well have some fun while I'm here!" (Translation by the Lynian Researcher) (Special ticket rewards)

quests.name: Mosswinin' and Dinin'
quests.description: The Admiral and Meowscular Chef trapped some Mosswine and put them into the Arena. I didn't have the courage to tell them, but those Mosswine look purr-ty odd to me. Take a look!

quests.name: Gaze Upon the Dawn
quests.description: Whenever I see Zorah Magdaros, I can't help but feel sad, and a bit homesick. Let's finish up our research so I can go back to the Old World and meet my master and former teammates again!

quests.name: Gajalaka Outbreak!
quests.description: Geez, I just wanted to study the Gajalaka language, so I brought a group of them with me, but they all ran away! Can you help me round them up before they get into trouble?

quests.name: Scrapping with the Shamos
quests.description: I'm getting bombarded with requests left n' right for the stuff I'm wearing, but I'm gonna need some special materials to meet demand. That's your cue, Hunter. You know what to do.

quests.name: A Flash in the Pan
quests.description: My dear sister and I were suffering from poor eyesight, but the Second Fleet Master crafted us some fine spectacles. I'll give mine to you if you help me test them out!

quests.name: Egg Lovers United
quests.description: While out gathering egg specimens, a familiar shadow took me unawares. But I believe we can use this for our own purposes! Study the Kulu-Ya-Ku's behavioral patterns, and report back!

quests.name: Wiggle Me This
quests.description: Wha--hey, don't throw that net on me, I'm not a Wiggler! Fooled you, eh? If you want something like what I'm wearing, then you'll have to help me with my research!

quests.name: Triple Threat Throwdown
quests.description: This is a quest that I've prepared...just for you. You won't believe how many decorations you'll get if you can complete this quest! Now, show me what you got!

quests.name: The Food Chain Dominator
quests.description: The Deviljho is a frightening presence that takes the idea of the food chain and crushes it between its massive jaws! Now it's here in the New World. It's time to get investigating!

quests.name: What Lurks In The Forest
quests.description: We can't lavish any more praise on a hunter such as yourself, who has survived the dangers of the New World. But we do have a quest that will challenge even you, our Sapphire Star!

quests.name: USJ Blazing Azure Stars!
quests.description: USJ is pleased to present the most EXPLOSIVE show ever! Our twin blue stars will show you a dance like you've never seen before! Complete our challenge, and earn some fantastic armor!

quests.name: A Rush of Blood
quests.description: Oh no! There's this big ol' monster that looks a lot like our Rush! Someone's gotta calm the big boy down! Help us out, and we'll give you some special gear for your Palico!

quests.name: This is How Revolts Start
quests.description: This is preposterous! Why can't I gather Kingly Cactus in peace!? This is beyond annoying, it's an uprising I tell you! Go out there and see for yourself

quests.name: Rock N' Roll Recess
quests.description: The monsters roaming the Elder's Recess seem intent on facing off with each other. This could be a huge boon for our research. Hunters, don't let this opportunity pass us by!

quests.name: Effluvial Opera
quests.description: The monsters roaming the Rotten Vale seem intent on facing off with each other. This could be a huge boon for our research. Hunters, don't let this opportunity pass us by!

quests.name: Coral Waltz
quests.description: The monsters roaming the Coral Highlands seem intent on facing off with each other. This could be a huge boon for our research. Hunters, don't let this opportunity pass us by!

quests.name: Wildspire Bolero
quests.description: The monsters roaming the Wildspire Waste seem intent on facing off with each other. This could be a huge boon for our research. Hunters, don't let this opportunity pass us by!

quests.name: Deep Green Blues
quests.description: The monsters lurking deep in the Ancient Forest seem intent on facing off with each other. This could be a huge boon for our research. Hunters, don't let this opportunity pass us by!

quests.name: Rollin' With The Uragaan
quests.description: Urk, my head is still spinning from what I just saw. We need someone to take out these troublemakers before anyone else gets queasy. Complete this quest for a lot of Armor Spheres!

quests.name: When Law Meets War
quests.description: Only a hunter like you, who has survived the dangers of the New World, can stand tall until the end and show everyone who has a heart that will not succumb to adversity!

quests.name: Deviljho Slay Event
